        "Retail_Inventory",
        "Connecting",
        "Connected",
        "Idle",
        "Sending"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，但Connecting还要考虑连接失败能回退到库存系统重试。另外关键一点：Idle和Sending都可能触发Timeout超时，超时后不能直接关闭，要流转到客户忠诚度系统做补偿处理。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Connecting",
        "Retail_Inventory",
        "Idle",
        "Sending",
        "Timeout",
        "Retail_CustomerLoyalty"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，我加上双向的Connecting回退，以及从Idle和Sending分别指向Timeout的分支，Timeout再连到客户忠诚度系统。还有正常关闭的路径吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Connecting",
        "Retail_Inventory",
        "Idle",
        "Sending",
        "Timeout",
        "Retail_CustomerLoyalty"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "有的，Idle状态下可以主动关闭连接，进入Closed终止态。Closed状态最终要流转到优惠券系统，表示会话结束后的营销触达。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Idle",
        "Closed",
        "Retail_CouponSystem"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加Idle到Closed，以及Closed到优惠券系统的流转。我检查一遍：库存系统起始于Connecting，可双向回退；成功后到Connected再到Idle；Idle可发数据到Sending，也可直接关闭到Closed；Sending完成回Idle，也可能超时；两个超时汇聚到客户忠诚度系统；关闭后进优惠券系统。",
      "elements_involved": [
